```

Pattern

```text
÷3

Answer = 1
```

---

### Example 3

```text
2 5 10 17 26 ?
```

Pattern

```text
1²+1

2²+1

3²+1

4²+1

5²+1

Answer = 37
```

---

### Example 4

```text
3 6 11 18 27 ?
```

Differences

```text
+3

+5

+7

+9

Next Difference

+11

Answer = 38
```

